longBusinessSummary: HolidayCheck Group AG engages in the transaction-based online business in the fields of travel and weather in Amsterdam, the Netherlands, Austria, Belgium, Poland, Germany, and Switzerland. It operates a range of hotel rating and holiday booking portals, which offer package tours, cruise, hotels, and rental car booking services; and Weer-Online.nl, an advertising based weather portal. The company also operates as a tour operator. The company was formerly known as TOMORROW FOCUS AG and changed its name to HolidayCheck Group AG in June 2016. HolidayCheck Group AG is headquartered in Munich, Germany. HolidayCheck Group AG is a subsidiary of Burda Digital SE.
